                <div class="FAQ">
                  <div class="fa">
                    <h3>
                      What should I do if my dryer is taking too long to dry
                      clothes?
                    </h3>
                  </div>

                  <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>

                  <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
